## Step 2 — Create Report Templates (exact fields)

### reports/PLAN_REPORT.template.md
- Objective
- Constraints
- Scope (in/out)
- Success Metrics
- Dependencies
- Risks
- Approval: [Manager]

### reports/DESIGN_REPORT.template.md
- Data Model Impact
- Objects Affected
- Interfaces (inputs/outputs)
- Failure Modes
- Validation Strategy
- Approval: [Planner + Manager]

### reports/BUILD_REPORT.template.md
- Objects Modified
- Logic Summary
- Assumptions
- Limitations
- Validation Queries Included: YES/NO

### reports/VALIDATION_REPORT.template.md
- Test Coverage
- Edge Cases
- Sample Outputs
- Pass/Fail Summary
- Blocking Issues

### reports/UX_REPORT.template.md
- Click Path
- Friction Points
- Failure Clarity
- Training Required
- Verdict: ACCEPT / REJECT / WARNING

### reports/RELEASE_REPORT.template.md
- Deployment Steps
- Rollback Plan
- Monitoring Plan
- Ownership
- Verdict: GO / NO-GO

